      "BR Guest Hospitality is passionate about creating the perfect dining experience for any occasion. They go all out for great tasting food accompanied by exceptional service. Their properties include Atlantic Grill, Bill’s Bar & Burger, Dos Caminos, Strip House, Metropolis, Blue Fin, Troy Liquor Bar, and Blue Water Grill, located in New York, Pittsburg, and Las Vegas; which recently became part of the Landry’s Inc. family.\r\n\r\nAtlantic Grill\r\nAtlantic Grill opened on the Upper East Side in 1998. Today, we are still a local favorite where you can enjoy fresh seafood dishes and our signature service in polished surroundings.  With restaurants in Manhattan (Upper East Side and near Lincoln Center), our fresh sushi, delectable raw bar and inventive dishes make for a standout culinary experience.\r\nBill’s Bar & Burger\r\nHome of the biggest standalone burger restaurant in the country, Bill’s Bar & Burger is your one-stop show for classic American fare. With locations in New York City and Pittsburgh, Bill’s provides a welcoming and low key space for guests to enjoy good company, sports games, great food and our extensive list of local and craft beers.  www.billsbarandburger.com\r\n\r\nBlue Fin\r\nBlue Fin is a modern seafood restaurant located at W New York – Times Square known for its oasis-like respite from the buzz of Times Square and top quality seafood and sushi. Blue Fin boasts an upscale feeling where Broadway energy meets quiet sophistication. The restaurant offers fresh, modern seafood and sushi to its devoted clientele of theater-goers, tourists and New York City seafood lovers alike.\r\nBlue Water Grill\r\nAfter a modern renovation, Blue Water Grill focuses on sustainability and highlighting local purveyors.  Enjoy our jaw-dropping dining room that complements historic architecture with contemporary touches.  The modern American seafood menu focuses on innovative, market fresh items.  A hidden gem - Metropolis is located in the old bank vault of the building.  Join us every Thursday night for Speakeasy Nights with live jazz music, dinner menu and cocktails. \r\nDos Caminos\r\nJoin the fiesta at one of New York City’s original Mexican restaurants! Dos Caminos features an expanded menu of authentic Mexican street food dishes as well as an extensive selection of premium tequilas and delicious, innovative cocktails. Experience the multi-regional modern cuisine for lunch, dinner and weekend brunch or enjoy happy hour weekdays from 3pm-6pm & 9pm-close\r\nStrip House\r\nStrip House, named one of New York’s best steak restaurants by Zagat and awarded four stars by Forbes, transports you back in time to a time of indulgence, class and luxury. As the ultimate steakhouse, you will experience the combination of charred cuts perfectly paired with decadent sides and superb wines and cocktails. Your dining experience is brought to life with siren red interiors where old world glamour meets modern style and sophistication.  \r\nwww.striphouse.com\r\n\r\nTroy\r\nCome take a walk on the wild side – girls, leave your Louis at home – and make your way into Troy Liquor Bar, a synergy of art, music, and fashion.  Troy Liquor Bar is a throwback to a simpler time, when there were hippies, not hipsters; when the Meatpacking District was a full blown meat market instead of a crazy champagne brunch; when it was about hanging out with your friends rather than snapping a selfie.  DJs will play to the crowd and spin vinyl while guests enjoy retro cocktails with house-made tinctures and bitters along with barrel-aged spirits.  The space is slick in design and features bold colored graffiti art by Col Wallnuts.  Kick back with friends in one of the five cozy nooks, shoot a game of pool or come by for a round of foosball.",
    redemptionInstructions:
      '**Redeem In-store**\r\n\r\n Using your eGift Card is simple: \r\n\r\n1. Print this page. \r\n2. Bring it into any participating Landry’s, Inc. location and present at time of payment. \r\nVisit www.landrysinc.com to find the nearest location. \r\n\r\nGUEST SUPPORT INFORMATION For Balance Inquiry call 1.888.345.8380. \r\n\r\nTERMS AND CONDITIONS: This Card is issued by MOCGC, Corp. and may be used to purchase goods and services at any participating Landry’s, Inc. or affiliated location in the U.S. until the full balance is used. The Card has no cash value; except as required by law, it is not redeemable for cash. Any resale is strictly prohibited. For balance information or to report your card lost or stolen call 1-888-345-8380. \r\nFor terms and conditions visit: www.landrysinc.com/giftcards/terms.asp. \r\n\r\nPLEASE TREAT THIS GIFT CARD LIKE CASH AND SAFEGUARD IT ACCORDINGLY. \r\n\r\nMANAGER INSTRUCTIONS: ALOHA MANAGER INSTRUCTIONS: On payment screen, touch "Gift Card" and key the e-Card number above. Swipe manager card for approval. Once on the check, return this paper to the guest. If any balance remains, they may re-use it until redeemed in full. \r\nFDegccorp 1.17',
